49
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:14,099
A son

50
00:03:14,180 --> 00:03:15,199
Do you have one?

51
00:03:15,199 --> 00:03:16,080
I do

52
00:03:17,939 --> 00:03:18,740
Son

53
