When I was little, I loved eating...

182
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,339
Fried mantou slices

183
00:07:28,339 --> 00:07:29,019
That's right!

184
00:07:30,620 --> 00:07:31,800
That's right!

185
00:07:32,819 --> 00:07:34,980
You really are Goushengzi

186
00:07:35,660 --> 00:07:36,339
Yes

187
