224
00:08:40,980 --> 00:08:42,220
I'm here.

225
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:43,179
Come.

226
00:08:44,299 --> 00:08:45,860
Have some tea.

227
00:08:45,860 --> 00:08:47,179
Xiao Lizi.

228
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:48,980
You're asking for a tea splashing, aren't you?

229
00:08:50,019 --> 00:08:51,679
I still don't understand.

230
00:08:51,860 --> 00:08:54,059
What exactly happened?

231
00:08:54,860 --> 00:08:55,899
That Gou'er Ye.

232
00:08:57,340 --> 00:08:58,940
Insisted I call him Dad.

233
00:08:59,779 --> 00:09:01,100
He can forget it.

234
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:04,340
