Alzheimer's.

240
00:09:13,980 --> 00:09:14,980
Al's Hammer.

241
00:09:15,220 --> 00:09:16,580
What kind of name is that?

242
00:09:16,820 --> 00:09:18,539
Not Al's Hammer.

243
00:09:18,580 --> 00:09:19,779
It's Alzheimer's.

244
00:09:19,779 --> 00:09:21,240
Alzheimer's.

245
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:23,399
Our German medical scientist.

246
00:09:24,460 --> 00:09:25,340
Your fellow countryman.

247
00:09:25,779 --> 00:09:26,940
He invented this disease.

248
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:27,500
Yes.

249
00:09:28,059 --> 00:09:28,860
No.

250
00:09:29,059 --> 00:09:30,779
How can a disease be invented?

251
00:09:30,779 --> 00:09:31,460
It was him...

252
