Designed...

253
00:09:33,460 --> 00:09:34,259
Developed...

254
00:09:34,259 --> 00:09:34,860
Dis...

255
00:09:34,860 --> 00:09:35,700
Discovered.

256
00:09:36,019 --> 00:09:36,820
Right.

257
00:09:36,899 --> 00:09:37,700
Discovered.

258
00:09:37,820 --> 00:09:39,700
He researched this disease.

259
00:09:40,220 --> 00:09:41,759
What's there to research?

260
00:09:42,059 --> 00:09:43,399
It's just getting senile.

261
