Look at him.

262
00:09:44,700 --> 00:09:45,980
Probably was stupid when he was young too.

263
00:09:45,980 --> 00:09:46,480
This disease...

264
00:09:46,559 --> 00:09:48,259
Has nothing to do with being stupid.

265
00:09:48,259 --> 00:09:50,200
Many high-IQ big shots...

266
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:51,679
Get it when they're old too.

267
00:09:51,860 --> 00:09:53,639
Like Reagan, Mrs. Thatcher.

268
00:09:53,860 --> 00:09:55,200
And there's that one...

269
00:09:55,659 --> 00:09:58,100
The Chinese scientist who won the Nobel Prize.

270
00:09:58,100 --> 00:09:58,899
Named Gao...

271
00:09:59,379 --> 00:10:00,460
Gao something... it's on the tip of my tongue.

272
00:10:00,460 --> 00:10:01,100
Look at you guys.

273
00:10:01,340 --> 00:10:02,720
He's about to get Alzheimer's.

274
00:10:03,899 --> 00:10:05,340
If anyone's getting it, it's you.

275
00:10:05,799 --> 00:10:06,860
Just like Gou'er Ye.

276
00:10:07,059 --> 00:10:08,580
It runs in your family, right?

277
00:10:08,580 --> 00:10:09,860
You're really asking for a tea splashing now.

278
00:10:10,860 --> 00:10:12,019
Stop it, you two brothers.

279
00:10:12,019 --> 00:10:12,700
Stop it.

280
00:10:12,899 --> 00:10:15,820
So Gou'er Ye isn't eating or drinking now, right?

281
00:10:15,980 --> 00:10:17,360
Just crying out for his son.

282
00:10:20,139 --> 00:10:20,940
President Li

283
00:10:21,580 --> 00:10:22,820
Could you...

284
00:10:23,139 --> 00:10:23,820
No.

285
00:10:24,460 --> 00:10:25,259
