286
00:10:25,620 --> 00:10:26,940
Absolutely not.

287
00:10:28,139 --> 00:10:29,259
Stop trying to persuade President Li.

288
00:10:29,419 --> 00:10:30,700
He's held a high position for years.

289
00:10:31,179 --> 00:10:32,960
To play the son of an old farmer...

290
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,580
can he handle that?

291
00:10:34,580 --> 00:10:36,139
This has nothing to do with rank.

292
00:10:36,139 --> 00:10:37,100
No, look...

293
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,559
Forget it.

294
00:10:39,059 --> 00:10:40,340
Let me say a few words.

