562
00:19:09,980 --> 00:19:11,059
You're rebellious.

563
00:19:11,940 --> 00:19:13,140
Think I'm an old fool?

564
00:19:13,140 --> 00:19:14,720
You just find anyone and...

565
00:19:14,900 --> 00:19:16,140
